<li id="cite_note-Powerful-50"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Powerful_50-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFStuart2018" class="citation journal cs1">Stuart, Joseph R. (September 2018). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.cambridge.org/core/journals/church-history/article/abs/more-powerful-effect-upon-the-body-early-mormonisms-theory-of-racial-redemption-and-american-religious-theories-of-race/6B910C6575F406655F36313AB5815270">"<span class="cs1-kern-left"></span>'A More Powerful Effect upon the Body': Early Mormonism's Theory of Racial Redemption and American Religious Theories of Race"</a>. <i><a href="/wiki/Church_History:_Studies_in_Christianity_and_Culture" class="mw-redirect" title="Church History: Studies in Christianity and Culture">Church History: Studies in Christianity and Culture</a></i>. <b>87</b> (3). <a href="/wiki/Cambridge_University_Press" title="Cambridge University Press">Cambridge University Press</a>: 27. <a href="/wiki/Doi_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="Doi (identifier)">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://doi.org/10.1017%2FS0009640718001580">10.1017/S0009640718001580</a>. <a href="/wiki/S2CID_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="S2CID (identifier)">S2CID</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://api.semanticscholar.org/CorpusID:165766064">165766064</a>. <q>These apostles [Orson Hyde and John Taylor] viewed skin color as an inescapable punishment for [B]lack Africans because of their own volition (premortal fence sitting) or their ancestors' choices (made by Ham or Cain).</q></cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Church+History%3A+Studies+in+Christianity+and+Culture&amp;rft.atitle=%27A+More+Powerful+Effect+upon+the+Body%27%3A+Early+Mormonism%27s+Theory+of+Racial+Redemption+and+American+Religious+Theories+of+Race&amp;rft.volume=87&amp;rft.issue=3&amp;rft.pages=27&amp;rft.date=2018-09&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1017%2FS0009640718001580&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fapi.semanticscholar.org%2FCorpusID%3A165766064%23id-name%3DS2CID&amp;rft.aulast=Stuart&amp;rft.aufirst=Joseph+R.&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cambridge.org%2Fcore%2Fjournals%2Fchurch-history%2Farticle%2Fabs%2Fmore-powerful-effect-upon-the-body-early-mormonisms-theory-of-racial-redemption-and-american-religious-theories-of-race%2F6B910C6575F406655F36313AB5815270&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3APremortal+life+%28Latter+Day+Saints%29" class="Z3988"></span></span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-Harris2015-51"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Harris2015_51-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Harris2015_51-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Harris2015_51-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Harris2015_51-3"><sup><i><b>d</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Harris2015_51-4"><sup><i><b>e</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFHarrisBringhurst2015" class="citation book cs1">Harris, Matthew L.; <a href="/wiki/Newell_G._Bringhurst" title="Newell G. Bringhurst">Bringhurst, Newell G.</a> (2015). <span class="id-lock-limited" title="Free access subject to limited trial, subscription normally required"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=Pn20CgAAQBAJ"><i>The Mormon Church and Blacks: A Documentary History</i></a></span>. Chicago: <a href="/wiki/University_of_Illinois_Press" title="University of Illinois Press">University of Illinois Press</a>. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0-252-08121-7" title="Special:BookSources/978-0-252-08121-7"><bdi>978-0-252-08121-7</bdi></a>. <link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><a href="/wiki/ProQuest_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ProQuest (identifier)">ProQuest</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://search.proquest.com/docview/2131052022">2131052022</a> &#8211; via <a href="/wiki/Google_Books" title="Google Books">Google Books</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Mormon+Church+and+Blacks%3A+A+Documentary+History&amp;rft.place=Chicago&amp;rft.pub=University+of+Illinois+Press&amp;rft.date=2015&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-252-08121-7&a